    "body": "Closes #5718\r\n\r\nMy reasoning is that we're using unstable Python API to build the code objects so it could change. That's unlikely to actually break anything so just return None and keep going if we can.\r\n\r\nAlso:\r\n* remove some 3.7 code\r\n* remove a bit of exception code (we no longer create these code objects during exception handling).",
